PrecisAppointment of DERRICK ROWE of St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador, as a Canadian representative to the General Council and to the Fisheries Commission of the Northwest Atlantic Fisheries Organization to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, effective February 7, 2005, in the place of John R.
